Script to change the btop hover over function. 

Now when the cursor is on the btop icon these values will appear (instead of the cores usage):

- CPU usage and temperature
- RAM usage
- GPU temperature

It is important to change the name of the module at the beggining of the cript ("modules-right") and in the style.css file (so that the icon shows fully). I wrote "personal-directory" in the place where the symbolic link to the sysinfo.sh should be (example= /home/usr-name/deskto/Waybar-Custom/sysinfo.sh)

DISCLAIMER: Only tested for AMD integrated GPU
